{"tid":1272194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《咪撚再分組討論塊玻璃》咪撚再問衝唔衝，只有你出定唔出","createTime":"2019-07-01T09:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T09:42:26.000Z","uid":265197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c685ef5aa0b8c562e84048f365254363d3f4227","tid":1272194,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"利申發緊夢<br />\n<br />\n就算去到企高位拍片都有可能幫到手做證據<br />\n唔好再理咩偉論最重要係你行唔行出呢個門口<br />\n唔出街就網上工作<br />\n出街逛就心理同生理都要準備十足<br />\n最易比人拉就係唔預自己會上到前線<br />\n但退唔切突然變左前線企係度騰晒雞果班<br />\n要確保自己係邊類人企緊咩位做緊乜野承擔到幾多野<br />\n現場執生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好陷入點解呢樣做咩果樣嘅小組討論陷阱<br />\n無人會問612點解個女人會企到咁前鬧差佬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住我地嘅五大訴求</span></span><br />\n暫緩負面情緒<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8697353efddc575e6c152e346fbf265a4b1dcc3","tid":1272194,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:33:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"234fd1374abc77429388edd68fccba5dd71fbe64","tid":1272194,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:34:36.000Z","msg":"絕對正常"},{"pid":"e6c86f1cd4f69cdec921da42b5529df8f80ce11c","tid":1272194,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:36:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"529b061049c4c12546414120e53a260978240e01","tid":1272194,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:42:26.000Z","msg":"push"}]}